data.description: Ask about the possibility of taking advantage of the SELLER’S LOAN ASSUMPTION with a FAVORABLE LOW INTEREST RATE. Step into luxury living with this stunning 4-bd, 3-ba home, boasting construction in 2021. Nestled in a new neighborhood with access to a fantastic school district, this residence offers the perfect blend of convenience and elegance. Located just minutes away from shopping, restaurants, and a mere 30-minute commute to the glistening shores of Corpus Christi Bay. Upon entry, you'll be greeted by the expansive living room with high ceilings, seamlessly flowing into the gorgeous kitchen. The centerpiece of this culinary haven is the impressive 12-foot kitchen island, perfect for gatherings and entertaining guests. The stylish subway tile backsplash adds a touch of sophistication to the space, complementing the s/s appliances. The pool size backyard has a large back patio that gives evening shade for all to enjoy the outdoor kitchen. This is a must see home.
